Introduction

Sury Su, formerly known as Su Ruiqi, is a Chinese singer, rapper, and dancer signed with ETM Skies. She used to be part of the C-Pop group Chic Chili and its sub-unit Chic Chili S&R.

She was a participant in the hit Korean survival show, Girls Planet 999 and Chinese survival shows Produce 101 China and Produce Camp 2020.
